Package: mender-gateway
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: mender-client
Description: Mender Gateway
 Mender Gateway exposes the Mender Device APIs to local devices
 running the Mender client and forwards the requests to an upstream
 Mender Server. It can optionally enhance the APIs with additional
 edge-specific features.
